{"word":"πληκτίζομαι","slug":"πληκτίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πληκτίζομαι</b></el> <el>(πληκτίζομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to bandy blows with</i> one, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to beat one's breast</i> for grief, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>plangere</el>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to indulge in dalliance</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}